        "schemeImageUrl": "",
        "detailedDescription_md": "The scheme &quot;Chief Minister Scholarship Scheme&quot; by the Education Department, Government of Gujarat, aims to encourage higher education by providing financial assistance to meritorious students who have passed Class 10th or Class 12th and secured admission in diploma, degree, or higher education courses. The scheme provides varying amounts of financial support based on the course type and merit.\n<br>\n\n",
        "benefits_md": "<br>\n\n**Benefit Type****Details of Assistance****Number of Beneficiaries**Financial Assistance for Medical and Dental CoursesUp to ₹5,00,000/-250 StudentsFinancial Assistance for Engineering/Technology, Pharmacy Diploma to Degree, Ayurveda/Homeopathy, Nursing, Physiotherapy, Para-medical CoursesUp to ₹1,00,000/-1,130 StudentsFinancial Assistance for Diploma CoursesUp to ₹50,000/-120 StudentsFinancial Assistance for Higher Education CoursesUp to ₹10,000/-1,000 Students<br>\n\n<br>\n\n",
        "briefDescription": "The scheme \"Chief Minister Scholarship Scheme\" by the Education Department, Government of Gujarat, aims to provide financial assistance to meritorious students for pursuing medical, engineering, diploma, and higher education courses.",
